Embraer, Cetip Added to Credit Suisse Brazil Model Portfolio

-- B y   N e y   H a y a s h i
-- 
2011-08-01T13:05:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/embraer-cetip-added-to-credit-suisse-brazil-model-portfolio.html
Embraer SA (EMBR3) , the world’s fourth-
largest planemaker, was added to Credit Suisse Group AG’s
“model portfolio” of Brazilian stocks after the company
reported “healthy” second-quarter earnings.  Brazilian clearinghouse  Cetip SA - Balcao Organizado de
Ativos e Derivativos (CTIP3)  and oil company  HRT Participacoes em
Petroleo SA (HRTP3)  were also added, Credit Suisse’s analyst Andrew T. Campbell wrote in a note to clients dated yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ney Hayashi in Sao Paulo at 
 ncruz4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos in New York at 
 papadopoulous@bloomberg.net  